text: Rimantė Kunickaitė (born 18 April 1993) is a Lithuanian footballer who played as a midfielder for A Lyga club FK Kauno Žalgiris. She has been a member of the Lithuania women's national team. ==References== Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football midfielders Category:Lithuanian women's footballers Category:Lithuania women's international footballers Category:Gintra Universitetas players
